        "subject": "LU-17000 contrib: add git-remote-status",
        "message": "LU-17000 contrib: add git-remote-status\n\nAdd a Git plugin in Python for monitoring remote repositories\nfor updates. This is motivated by Coverity; the build submission\nprocess is still mostly manual and requires an easy monitoring\nmethod to know when to kick off new builds.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: I2b522b3f9e4ce559d068d99b9088e857bdd14b6b\n"
